{"id": "1445285273465520218", "channel_id": "1439936264911720479", "type": 0, "author_id": "1438532571947597976", "author_name": "santianliangjuesleep", "author_bot": false, "content": "还差三只诞墨<:thinking2:1356053172065534153>", "timestamp": "2025-12-02T05:27:41.296000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1439936264911720479", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "新手求助", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
{"id": "1445416838208164113", "channel_id": "1445416838208164113", "type": 0, "author_id": "404645235197607939", "author_name": "wilson_1024", "author_bot": false, "content": "第1队是以鸟哥鸟弟为主，医生负责银饰充能开觉醒，剩下1个位置打算塞温可尔解决狂气问题。\n但是塞了 雷亚 后可以获得血胎来解决狂气，而且鸟哥也可以吃到新密契的“卡牌进入空间加血肉进度”的效果来加速自身的狂气。\n然后主流配队大多数是塞 诗人 的，可是我的 诗人 塞了进去 第二队打反击流，主要是诗人有“反击提升”和降力效果。\n然后第3张图就是我其他的一些辅助，目前无就业空间\n所以鸟哥鸟弟带什么辅助好啊", "timestamp": "2025-12-02T14:10:28.775000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1445416839315198026", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-12-02-21-52-01-270_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 219159, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1445416838208164113/1445416839315198026/Screenshot_2025-12-02-21-52-01-270_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69cd2755&is=69cbd5d5&hm=aa82d5b3be12bf08cf2866037d52a45ed36cd4b610fe01641446e70eead4a1f9&"}, {"id": "1445416840410038322", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-12-02-21-52-04-670_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 209404, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1445416838208164113/1445416840410038322/Screenshot_2025-12-02-21-52-04-670_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69cd2755&is=69cbd5d5&hm=40187245fb8c348c0e6f970bf6b26e0a0467cb7c69ca7f5857c0a7e38e6e2f02&"}, {"id": "1445416841244573708", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-12-02-21-54-15-621_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 192175, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1445416838208164113/1445416841244573708/Screenshot_2025-12-02-21-54-15-621_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69cd2755&is=69cbd5d5&hm=62af34070ef3afc95b32c63d35d1aa45b7a77f5583b9f49f29dc059b71bfe74f&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1445416838208164113", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "融灾配队（辅助疑惑）", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
