{"id": "1445466565406625961", "channel_id": "1445416838208164113", "type": 0, "author_id": "862713193885335602", "author_name": "bailuk", "author_bot": false, "content": "哈姆林/奧爾拉/熔燬·朵爾/克萊門汀/溫柯爾，次選艾瑞卡/詹金", "timestamp": "2025-12-02T17:28:04.663000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-02T17:29:54.649000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1445416838208164113", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "融灾配队（辅助疑惑）", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
{"id": "1445474775190208594", "channel_id": "1445416838208164113", "type": 0, "author_id": "862713193885335602", "author_name": "bailuk", "author_bot": false, "content": "阿格里帕也可以，靠阿格里帕開大疊戒備增加黑羽的保留護盾，輸出就靠波呂克斯慢慢磨，這時最後一人因為隊伍缺少易傷推薦選艾瑞卡，克萊門汀就可以留給其他隊伍", "timestamp": "2025-12-02T18:00:42.028000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-02T18:32:19.518000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1445416838208164113", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "融灾配队（辅助疑惑）", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
{"id": "1445496884691996852", "channel_id": "1445416838208164113", "type": 0, "author_id": "862713193885335602", "author_name": "bailuk", "author_bot": false, "content": "卡斯托爾的密契可以改用扭曲雙子·白，每回合第一張指令卡觸發卡斯托爾的超距拿黑羽，黑羽保留在手牌疊護盾，狂氣問題通過打出打擊防禦牌、卡斯托爾的二啟與進超維空間觸發專屬命輪的回狂效果解決", "timestamp": "2025-12-02T19:28:33.344000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1445416838208164113", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "融灾配队（辅助疑惑）", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
{"id": "1445334431920296027", "channel_id": "1445334431920296027", "type": 0, "author_id": "1139202390919233566", "author_name": "akkom730", "author_bot": false, "content": "咳咳…我…我不行了\n剩下的…就交給你了！(趴\n\n媽呀我討厭破眼球\n不要吃我狂啦，我沒狂開大啊啊啊\n\n建議攻略：\n老招\n借一隻塔薇(70等有超限)+3隻廢物\n# 3隻廢物\n然後密契塞上去，具體作用不是很重要，大方向為銀鑰疊高就好\n\n# 講點操作的問題\n這波的眼球效果是\n每回合減少我方10狂，回870左右的血\n如果沒有穩定的狂氣收入，你開不了大(自己回合結束+5狂對面吃你10狂，我狂啊<:takenotes:1357186646294138890> \n造物功能是大招出傷強化，每次開大依照消耗狂氣量給銀鑰，並減少狂氣上限20(最多5次\n\n我是非主C有狂就開，每隊盡量塞一隻自充很快的角色\n覺醒先給塔薇，接下來等開第一次大(超限)再慢慢覺醒其他人\n\n如果隊伍操作不夠熟悉會打很久，我平均10t以上到14t", "timestamp": "2025-12-02T08:43:01.585000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1445334432830722168", "filename": "IMG_4511.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1171850, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1445334431920296027/1445334432830722168/IMG_4511.png?ex=69ccda95&is=69cb8915&hm=8f9b1c30a82cce597777061fe58c153730a71a7136f16fefb52708da2e1b69bb&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1445334431920296027", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "大眼球D2", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
{"id": "1445334938923696220", "channel_id": "1445334431920296027", "type": 0, "author_id": "1139202390919233566", "author_name": "akkom730", "author_bot": false, "content": "圖片是便宜大招\n只要60、70、60、70狂就可以開大\n後面會打的比較開心一點", "timestamp": "2025-12-02T08:45:02.464000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1445334431920296027", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "大眼球D2", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
